cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "nemetonshiny: Shiny front-end for the Nemeton systemic forest analysis platform"
abstract: >
  Interactive Shiny/golem application for the Nemeton systemic forest
  analysis platform. Provides project management, indicator radar
  visualisation, per-family dashboards, QField field workflow
  (export plan + import returned field data), OAuth2 authentication
  and LLM-powered expert profiles. Depends on the nemeton core
  package for business logic; contains no business logic of its own
  (ADR-009).
